  @5
  The  cop  was quite polite and wasn't cocky at all,  I got a bit embarrassed
  when my boss came out to have a look at what was going on but he wasn't  too
  fussed. After asking me to press the brake, lights, reverse etc he asked me:
  @7
                    "Do you know anything about these lights?"
  @3
            "................ er,  a ,          ... U,......... erm?!"
  @7
